{
  "stem": "1918.6",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 260.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it was a-- these were soldiers who fought for five years, six years, and they never had a furlough, unlike the Western armies.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And when they went home finally, they found their homes burned up and their families murdered.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And it was rough.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was hard.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We understood, them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Luckily we were able to escape their advances, and we didn't get raped.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There were tents, and some of them were caught in it, and others were able to escape it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, related, in a more humorous way, when they came in the-- when they came in in the morning to get us to go to work, I was so afraid of getting raped that-- and by this time, I was quite lovely, because I gained weight, you know.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I would-- I would put on a torn socks full of holes on my shaved head, which was-- the hair was beginning to grow.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And stuck out my tongue and put my eyes one eye up and one eye down and made believe that I can't walk straight, that I'm crippled, and had my hands in a funny way.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Anything to escape being raped.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I did escape it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I made myself look like the Hunchback of Notre Dame.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we escaped it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And then we were put-- then we were told that we have to leave, because there is no more food in the area, and we have to make our way home.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "There was only one train in this war-torn land in a place called Oelsk.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And we marched, as everybody did, for two weeks on the road, all the liberated people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we kept yelling, as everybody else did, have you seen my mother, my father, my sister, my brother?",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
